`Footer` is called with an `attribution` prop and `appConfig.footer.attribution`, but the `Footer` component expects `showAttribution` and the `AppConfig` schema defines `footer.showUnblocksAttribution` (no `attribution` field). This will fail type-checking; update the prop name and source field to match the actual config shape.
